==English==
===Etymology===
Blend of "[[natural|nat(ural)]] [[language|lang(uage)]]", by analogy with [[conlang]].

===Noun===
'''natlang''' (''Plural:'' [[natlangs]])
#(''[[constructed language|conlanging]]'') a [[natural]] [[language]], one that arose without intentional design (''Antonym:'' [[conlang]])

